  "detailed_description": "Run jump and shoot through various locations as Robot-X in this platforming shooter. Robot-X is 1 of 26 robots forged for battle, but when they are activated to protect the city, only one awakens: Robot-X. Robot-X must fight off evil and discover what went wrong on this retro journey. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/2352da276e37d29c5ab9d43bc8bd0399.poster.avif?t=1735585988\" width=498 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/2352da276e37d29c5ab9d43bc8bd0399.webm?t=1735585988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>have a friend join with a second controller in local co-op as Tin Can! Tin Can is Robot-X's sidekick built from scraps and coffee cans. (Requires 2 controllers)<br><br>     -7-ish Areas Each With Boss Battles!<br>     -Over 10 Unique Boss battles<br>     -Roughly 30 levels (give or take)<br>     -Boss Rush<br>     -Challenge Mode, with remixed level designs<br>     -Speedrun Timer built in<br>     -Simple Plot With Lore<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/e63d9065736262cbaaf748aad14f2991.poster.avif?t=1735585988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/e63d9065736262cbaaf748aad14f2991.webm?t=1735585988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/e63d9065736262cbaaf748aad14f2991.mp4?t=1735585988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>challenging but forgiving (and not rage inducing) Platformer-Shooter gameplay.<br>retro Inspired Gameplay!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/c67eed6ce807c001fd520bd3e3f86023.poster.avif?t=1735585988\" width=540 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/c67eed6ce807c001fd520bd3e3f86023.webm?t=1735585988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923380/extras/c67eed6ce807c001fd520bd3e3f86023.mp4?t=1735585988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>pixel perfect graphics (no halfway overlapping or diagonal pixels here)<br><br>WISHLIST IT NOW!!!",
